<Base
  title="Fractional IT Manager in Japan: The Complete Guide for SMEs : MKUltraman"
  description="What a fractional IT manager does, what it costs vs a full-time hire in Japan, when  to engage one, and how  to evaluate candidates. A definitive guide for foreign-owned and Japanese SMEs."
